arStrings.szText: You are a priest of Rathma. Or trained in their way.
You are a Child of Bul-Kathos. Or trained in their way.
You are a student of the Zann Esu. Or trained in their way.
I recognize your charms! You are learned in the Scéal Fada.
You are trained in the way of the Sightless Eye.
I see it in the shallowness of your breath. We learned much from your order.
(chuckles) Sure-footed, kind-hearted. I hope to visit Mount Arreat someday – see the Worldstone with my own eyes.
I am Yshari, myself. I’d always hoped our clans would convene more often. Debates were lively, but never petty. Quite the rarity in Caldeum.
I never thought I’d meet a king of the Glen! Few come to Caldeum these days, and no wonder. Intolerance abounds.
I see it in the lightness of your step. I hear the Sisters have thrived in Khanduras.
